summary:
Comes with both Quality & Performance version.
Colors are balanced between saturated and desaturated to provide a more native feel for the game this is the best enb for you if you love spring and autumn colors which is more vibrant and natural.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://i37.tinypic.com/2yzd5ih.jpg[/img]
[line]
[img]http://i47.tinypic.com/1zb8b50.jpg[/img]
- This Enb was optimized for CoT but you can also use it without that mod and this Enb provides a more native feel for the game thus adapting the colors of spring and autumn which is more vibrant and natural.Comes with both Quality & Performance version and SweetFX Presets.


[img]http://i46.tinypic.com/wv798y.jpg[/img]
- Enb d3d9.dll v0.132
[url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0132.htm]Download d3d9.dll file here[/url]
- d3d9.dll v0.132 Bugs:
Ambient Conclusion in Thick Fogs
Sky Lightning[I\'ve already fixed it so don\'t change the sky lightning value from enbseries.ini]


[img]http://i45.tinypic.com/xbn7nc.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i38.tinypic.com/34791cw.jpg[/img]


[img]http://i45.tinypic.com/nyz1he.jpg[/img]
- [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17802]Climates Of Tamriel[/url]
- [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17168]Skyrim Bigger Trees[/url]
- [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27043]Enchanced LIghts and FX[/url]
- [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/141]Flora Overhaul[/url]
- [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30450/]Realistic Lightning Overhaul[/url]
- [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/521]Sparkle Lush Environment Pack[/url]
- [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/1892]Sparkle Lush Cities Pack[/url]
- [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13531]Ultra Realistic World Lightning[/url]
[line]

[img]http://i35.tinypic.com/50r1fq.jpg[/img]
- Copy all files from \"Hawks Embrace Enb - CoT v0.2b Core\" to your skyrim folder.
- Choose between Performance Or Quality inside the \"Enb Settings\" folder.
- Choose your SweetFX preset from \"Sweet Fx Presets\" folder and replace the one in \"Hawks Embrace Enb - CoT v0.2b Core\\SweetFX\\Presets\"
[line]
